==English==
===Etymology===
''[[xeno-]]'' "foreign" + ''[[-onym]]'' "name"
===Noun===
'''xenonym'''

#A name for a people or a language which is not used by the people themselves. For example, ''[[German]]'' is a xenonym for a people who call themselves ''[[Deutsche|Deutsche]]''.

